 .app-shell {
   display: grid;
-  grid-template-rows: var(--header-height) 1fr var(--footer-height);
+  /* CRITICAL: Use a *definite* height so the middle `1fr` track can actually
+     constrain `.app-body` and make it the scroll container (instead of the page).
+     Without this, iOS/WebKit ends up scrolling the document, which triggers
+     viewport reflows + canvas resizes → janky/flickery rendering. */
